{"tid":1933293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譚德塞:超過80%的病例來自西太平洋和歐洲這兩個區域。","createTime":"2020-03-19T08:06:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T14:30:11.000Z","uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"87828c49e59411a1806cb1c45a58b2ddae958199","tid":1933293,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:06:32.000Z","msg":"大家下午好。 &nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n 剛果民主共和國最後一例埃博拉病例已經過去一個多月了。 如果這樣保持下去，將在不到一個月的時間內宣布疫情結束。 &nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n 我們要感謝所有的合作夥伴，感謝他們團結一心堅持到底，為剛果人民服務。 我還要特別感謝剛果民主共和國政府和人民。 &nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n 我們必鬚髮揚同樣的團結精神，戰勝COVID-19。 &nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n 世衛組織收到20多萬例COVID-19病例報告，有8000多人喪生。 &nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"color: red;\">超過80%的病例來自西太平洋和歐洲這兩個區域。</span> &nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.who.int/zh/dg/speeches/detail/who-director-general-s-opening-remarks-at-the-media-briefing-on-covid-19---18-march-2020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fzh%2Fdg%2Fspeeches%2Fdetail%2Fwho-director-general-s-opening-remarks-at-the-media-briefing-on-covid-19---18-march-2020&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFanyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=4be1d0fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.who.int/zh/dg/speeches/detail/who-director-general-s-opening-remarks-at-the-media-briefing-on-covid-19---18-march-2020</a>"},{"pid":"6f89b19ccc5240418a71b541b5d366c21497bb93","tid":1933293,"uid":201604,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:07:44.000Z","msg":"因為中國已經停止檢驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"874ac9887e82c91f5581186e0b0998db68dbc249","tid":1933293,"uid":337723,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:07:49.000Z","msg":"其餘20% 已經係武漢焚化爐燒緊, <br />\n燒埋就連20%都無埋"},{"pid":"cbd8cb7acfbb9a591b437bddb0fea71ff5bfa8d0","tid":1933293,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:09:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ShoKhSJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i